{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":13192,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":2407,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"啊这","timestamp":1592810519,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13244,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":2407,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"打左灯向右转","timestamp":1592810900,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13341,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":2407,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"社会割裂得严重 往往只能看到和自己相同阶级境遇的状况 底层发声困难 再加上言论审核 宣传部门\n无声的人是大多数","timestamp":1592811538,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13346,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":2407,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"基尼系数这几年已经说不清了\n中国大部分人可能都不知道什么是基尼系数","timestamp":1592811588,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13361,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":2407,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"清华学子还能关心社会的现状\n大部分人恐怕连获取信息都很难\n遑论发声","timestamp":1592811653,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13388,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":2407,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 唉\n","timestamp":1592811855,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13610,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":2407,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"火车不动了\n……………\n勃涅日列夫：“同志们，不如我们上下晃动，装作这个火车还在向前走吧！”","timestamp":1592813069,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13623,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":2407,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"基尼系数作为收入/财产分布的函数，是个上凸函数[1]，也就是说将两个地区的收入/财产按人口加权平均之后，得到的基尼系数会比两个基尼系数的加权平均值更高。所以人口多的国家/地区的基尼系数容易更大。\n\n[1] Zagier, Don. \"Inequalities for the Gini coefficient of composite populations.\" Journal of Mathematical Economics 12.2 (1983): 103-118.","timestamp":1592813175,"type"